An issue I ran into was the chart was showing perfectly in IE and Chrome, but not in Firefox. 

We had some code that dealt with formatting in the tickFormatter and we relied on .innerText, but Firefox uses .textContent.
This was causing the chart to not appear. 

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/24427621/innertext-vs-innerhtml-vs-label-vs-text-vs-textcontent-vs-outertext
http://perfectionkills.com/the-poor-misunderstood-innerText/
http://www.kellegous.com/j/2013/02/27/innertext-vs-textcontent/


